snippet.title: Divisibility By 11
snippet.description: Here is a second video on the rule for testing divisibility by 11. Is the reverse of a multiple of 11 again a multiple of eleven? (Yes) Is every even palindrome a multiple of 11? (Yes). If abcdef is a multiple of 11, then so is badcfe !!
